_model: sprints
---
title: Sprints at EuroSciPy 2026
---
body:

### Joined Sprints with EuroPython

This years sprints will happen on July 18 and 19, 2026.
We we are happy to announce that we joined with EuroPython.
You can find all relevant information at the
[EuroPython site](https://ep2026.europython.eu/sprints/).
